00:16:35,958 --> 00:16:38,791
- IT WILL FEEL A LITTLE COLD,
BUT JUST GIVE IT A LITTLE TIME,

234
00:16:38,875 --> 00:16:41,166
AND IT WILL ADJUST
TO YOUR BODY TEMPERATURE.

235
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:42,708
JUST TAKE YOUR TIME
AND MAKE SURE THAT ALL

236
00:16:42,791 --> 00:16:44,750
OF THE CONNECTIONS MATCH UP.

237
00:16:47,083 --> 00:16:48,583
- OH. COLD.

238
00:16:52,875 --> 00:16:53,875
- GOOD.

239
00:16:53,958 --> 00:16:57,083
NOW LEAN FORWARD
AND PUT YOUR ARMS IN.

240
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,750
- WHAT NOW?

241
