- WAIT.  I'M RELEASING YOU
FROM THE HANGER.

242
00:17:30,041 --> 00:17:31,458
- ( gasping )

243
00:17:37,583 --> 00:17:40,791
IT LOOKED HEAVY,
BUT IT'S REALLY LIGHT.

244
00:17:47,208 --> 00:17:50,583
- IT'S DANGEROUS TO MOVE AROUND
LIKE THAT IN THE BEGINNING.

245
00:17:50,666 --> 00:17:52,500
YOU HAVE TO GET USED
TO IT GRADUALLY.

246
00:17:52,583 --> 00:17:55,666
- WOW! ( laughing )

247
00:17:57,083 --> 00:17:59,333
- Hey, Sylia,
we got a rogue boomer in 24.

248
00:18:05,458 --> 00:18:09,083
- I KNEW THESE NEW FEMALE MODELS
WERE GOING TO BE TROUBLE.

249
00:18:09,166 --> 00:18:11,625
