250
00:18:11,708 --> 00:18:14,541
TO DRIVE THE MOBILE PIT OUT
TO WHERE PRISS IS.

251
00:18:14,625 --> 00:18:16,500
- WE DON'T HAVE
THAT MUCH TIME.  SUIT UP.

252
00:18:16,583 --> 00:18:18,833
- ME?  ALL BY MYSELF?

253
00:18:18,916 --> 00:18:22,208
