267
00:19:26,791 --> 00:19:29,541
- ACTUALLY, WE NORMALLY
PUT OUR SUITS ON IN HERE,

268
00:19:29,625 --> 00:19:31,083
BUT SINCE THIS WAS
YOUR FIRST TIME,

269
00:19:31,166 --> 00:19:32,875
